content.description: At Kin Khao’s fashionable baby sister restaurant, tucked inside Hotel Kabuki, Chef/owner Pim Techamuanvivit infuses her bold, vibrant Thai cooking with a thoroughly modern Californian sensibility—sliced fresh stone fruit in a Massaman lamb curry, for instance. The result is delicious, elegantly composed food in an equally sleek setting. Kick ...
